Rail Passes, penal action for false information, modification of vacancies, mode of selection, conduct of CBT, allotment of 
examination centers, selection, allotment of posts to selected candidates etc., will be final and binding on the candidates 
and no enquiry or correspondence will be entertained by the RRBs in this regard.

18.3 RRBs will not be responsible for any inadvertent errors.

18.4 Any legal issues arising out of this CEN shall fall within the legal jurisdiction of respective Central Administrative 
Tribunals under which the RRB concerned is located. 

